{
  "stem": "3100.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, by the night end, they took them away to a non-disclosed place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- it took us a long time to find out from the Polacks that they took the transport to Belzec, which was not far from-- it was also, I think, in the Lublin [POLISH],",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's in the Lublin District.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I didn't have an idea what the Belzec place is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, they told us that it's a camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only to find out later that this was the first of places that the German SS has organized to bring people there and to finish them off in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't take too long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was called in for about a month.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to go to work to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then one day, I was told I have to get into a group of people, and they took us to a park.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They called it P Park, near the Bahnhof station or railroad station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were already-- we couldn't leave that place anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we stood there for about two months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And while they were-- while they-- it happened while we were there is that they-- and closer to when in October or the high holidays-- they had another [GERMAN], which means Krasnik had to become judenrein, free of Jews.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, the Judenrat has organized a little camp in Krasnik, and there were left a few people there that worked.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some-- some workers that could produce like shoe makers, and tailors, and you know, craftsmanship-- a few.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they needed them to do something.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
